rows.label: tlk006101_05_msg0001
rows.name:
There's a lot of nice people here in
Avaritia.

rows.label: tlk006101_05_msg0002
rows.name:
I've been helping out at the docks for
a while, but Garram only recently told
me why we have to do work like this.

rows.label: tlk006101_05_msg0003
rows.name:
It's so that we can get familiar with
Avaritia, and build up our stamina
and endurance.

rows.label: tlk006101_05_msg0004
rows.name:
I think I can work hard knowing that
it's for good people. I need to return
the kindness they showed me.
